The association UDF raises the tone and sums up the New Center to no longer use its acronym
The UDF association, controlled by the MoDem of François Bayrou, reacted on Friday to the APO attempt of the president of the New Centre, Hervé Morin, under the acronym of the former Giscardian party, urging him to no longer use it on any support, under penalty of prosecution.
