You have multiplied, in recent days, the statements indicating that you will propose to your political movement to +take over + the acronym UDF, the association writes in a letter signed by 19 of the 24 members of the bureau, including François Bayrou and Marielle de Sarnez of the MoDem, as well as Senator Jean Arthuis of the Centrist Alliance.
