Its body is in two dimensions with creepy colors.
Earth's attraction no longer has power over it, it hovers at the edge of the ceiling.
He feels a blow.
Behind him winged devil creatures, grinding, bloody mouth, showing teeth.
They chase him, kick him with heavy flamboyant boots, throw him against the walls, he feels pain all over his body.
Toning, mean voices, screaming, coming out of the walls and the radio.
He can no longer stand those voices that insult and humiliate him.
Henning T. pulls two cables out of his stereo chain, makes it a loop and attaches it to a hook attached to the ceiling.
He climbs on a baffle and loops around his neck.
